{"tid":626950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強吻]香港女記者同外國女記者分別 港女真係正臭雞","createTime":"2018-04-12T14:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T15:42:41.000Z","uid":47132,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"acd737111afc2b2cb70680092dc304242ab32b83","tid":626950,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"港女記者同外國女記者分別 港女真係正臭雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cable_2712162275acdad6aaa48a-335x256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fcable_2712162275acdad6aaa48a-335x256.jpg&h=e52bf38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1351920/org/d95bf38c776942ffdce87439fc9cf620.png/P0xYhz5WK3mF1CAG2HeUV7-7VNzGF8d1aPJyN2jycjc?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1351920%2Forg%2Fd95bf38c776942ffdce87439fc9cf620.png%2FP0xYhz5WK3mF1CAG2HeUV7-7VNzGF8d1aPJyN2jycjc%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=7f58e5ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180411/0d8d3bc099fc41f8aba0f78fc528bf10.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180411%2F0d8d3bc099fc41f8aba0f78fc528bf10.gif&h=b12a495c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西一名31歲的體育記者迪爾特里（Bruna Dealtry），日前在一場球賽賽後進行直播訪問時，突然被一名在場的男性球迷強吻。之後迪爾特里仍鎮定地進行直播，事後她將該段視頻發上臉書，憤怒寫下「我是一個記者，我是一個女人，我應該得到尊重」，該文引發網友熱議，也引來其他女記者的響應，她們製作了一個1分鐘的影片，紀錄記者們在攝影機前遭到性騷擾的事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，迪爾特里在3月14日於臉書上傳一則視頻，影片可見她在某場直播訪問中，突然被一名赤裸上身的男性球迷強吻，雖然她看似鎮定繼續進行訪問，但心裡不甘受辱，因此上網發文。<br />\n<br />\n迪爾特里在文內寫下自己對於身為記者一職感到驕傲，她不介意與粉絲同歡、泡啤酒浴，或被粉絲不小心踩到腳，然而如今卻在沒有她的允許之下，被陌生男子公然性騷擾，「今天，我親身體驗到不少女性在球場、地鐵甚至在街上行走時感受到的無力感」，她認為該男子無視她對自身職業的重視。<br />\n<br />\n迪爾特里寫下「那位無理的騷擾者，應該為他所做的事感到羞愧。我是一名足球記者，我也是一名女性，我理應得到尊重」，該事件引發網友討論，更引來許多女記者撻伐該男子的作為，52名女記者決定起身反抗，她們製作了1分鐘的影片，影片內紀錄記者在攝影機前被騷擾的事件，貼上主題標籤「#deixaelatrabalhar」，在葡萄牙文中意即「讓她做自己的工作」（#LetHerDoHerJob）。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友留言聲援迪爾特里，「這個舉動實在令人厭惡」、「這個男人不懂尊重」，有人讚賞迪爾特里在令人作嘔的騷擾後依然專業的繼續訪問。該事件促使巴西體育部和國家婦女政策秘書處發起反性騷運動，鼓勵女性運動員們說出自己在體育行業中受到的騷擾。"},{"pid":"df2434a90576d4e67fdceecf350ea88428380415","tid":626950,"uid":65774,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:19:44.000Z","msg":"望下兩張圖既男人差幾遠先啦"},{"pid":"ec0e79193737338626bd8af2d9129bf18274bb9d","tid":626950,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"港女愛洋腸是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fad9b9bf3ecc7c6a31a4045dc6a96e195fbd55","tid":626950,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"試吓換成碧咸同C7"},{"pid":"67eb50d1a093768a17eec71c3c6c106e8a24fe2c","tid":626950,"uid":71100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7fad9b9bf3ecc7c6a31a4045dc6a96e195fbd55","tid":626950,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"試吓換成碧咸同C7"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"啲水流到去銅鑼灣避風塘"},{"pid":"791a9aeb747e5fadbfe59ae7d12e6ec1677df20a","tid":626950,"uid":22932,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"外國女記者個幕就等於<br />\n香港女記者俾個油頭毒撚錫一樣反應<br />\n但香港個個好彩俾個靚仔洋腸錫"},{"pid":"c3648d0af6c8b56b66b1b8abccca5b1b7153efb2","tid":626950,"uid":178332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"下面嗰件真心唔掂囉<br />\n重有啤酒肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01ca943c5f56d9a5392b874bafc62f70c31ed29","tid":626950,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"靚仔=文化差異<br />\n柒頭=性騷擾"},{"pid":"dba859fcc665798c5013a53e2832b073ede73d51","tid":626950,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"崇洋港女個閪=<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/232031_a9ad5cb0c8f5dd471767fecbc8381cb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F232031_a9ad5cb0c8f5dd471767fecbc8381cb5.png&h=c1614d00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"108ecce533ec740e08d70febbe90b4d9945b4991","tid":626950,"uid":152209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"791a9aeb747e5fadbfe59ae7d12e6ec1677df20a","tid":626950,"uid":22932,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"外國女記者個幕就等於<br />\n香港女記者俾個油頭毒撚錫一樣反應<br />\n但香港個個好彩俾個靚仔洋腸錫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都被你看透"},{"pid":"5cfbf314f05e11575bc215df02fb7cbcf9b9119e","tid":626950,"uid":164913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"264dcb60a59bae36840c5029cdd8a7d475c0c07e","tid":626950,"uid":82436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"Sources?<br />\n依幾句係有香港老婆嘅白人寫？"},{"pid":"f5d8d79bb6a22d01e827a91085c0f9b07e4fe739","tid":626950,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}